âš ï¸ Security Analysis
Issue	Risk Description
Unencrypted Traffic	Both services use HTTP, allowing sensitive data to be intercepted in transit.
Weak Authentication	Basic Auth can be brute-forced or sniffed, especially if default creds are used.
IoT Exposure	Devices like Sunny WebBox often have known vulnerabilities if not updated.
Global Access	No IP-based access control or firewall protection visible on these ports.

ğŸ” Recommendations
Area	Recommended Action
ğŸ”‘ Authentication	Change default credentials; consider disabling Basic Auth entirely
ğŸ”’ Encryption	Enable HTTPS using valid TLS certificates
ğŸš« Access Control	Use a firewall or router rules to block external access to ports 88 and 8000
ğŸ§° Updates	Regularly update the firmware of Sunny WebBox and webcam systems
ğŸ§± Network Design	Place devices behind a VPN or isolate them on a private internal network
ğŸ§ª Monitoring	Periodically audit using Shodan or similar tools to check for accidental exposure

